name: Lucid dream in Mazunte #02
description: Mazunte is a hidden gem on the Pacific coast of southern Mexico. I got inspired by a Mexican photographer during my travel and worked a lot on the color painting technique. This one is the second of the series: ”Lucid dream in Mazunte” I wanted to tell the amazing feeling that I have through the vibe of beaches, sunsets, people, and nightlife of this small hipster town.
